* Snow Depth @ Polygon Center [585825.60E 7910303.16N] UTM Zone 4&#xD;
* Snow Depth @ Polygon Trough [585829.02E 7910307.70N] UTM Zone 4&#xD;
Site B is located on polygonal permafrost and co-located with micromet surface measurements and subsurface measurements.&#xD;
&#xD;
